### Get all cars (default pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/cars HTTP/1.1

### Get all cars (custom pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/cars?page=1&result=10 HTTP/1.1

### Get car by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/cars/66c73beb2cfe5525c3337dec HTTP/1.1

### Create car
POST http://localhost:5000/api/cars HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "brand": "New car brand",
    "model": "New car model",
    "year": 2000,
    "color": "New car color",
    "engine_type": "New car engine type",
    "bodywork_type": "New car bodywork type",
    "gear_type": "New car gear type",
    "new": false,
    "logo": null,
    "type": "Truck"
}

